{"tid":1712683,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黑警屠殺中大係想令天日罷工唔成功！！！！（急推）","createTime":"2019-11-12T15:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T01:08:37.000Z","uid":125760,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"bab758605b0fd0a4ea4e5ddb41f7797dbf909091","tid":1712683,"uid":125760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"正式宣佈：11.13 晨曦行動 繼續罷 ! 繼續塞 !<br />\n<br />\n我係度向各位暴大手足致敬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明日因為暴大要守城，各區一定會少左好多人幫手塞路。到時黑警就可以成功阻止罷工，暴大手足頭破血流啦。<br />\n所以要靠我地啊！！！</span></span>,之前無出黎既請一定要出黎，唔好比黑警分散注意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11.13晨曦行動 !!!<br />\n<br />\n今日各區已經全面開花為罷工開路!!<br />\n<br />\n成條馬路上既既交通燈打得既已經打晒!!<br />\n<br />\n聽日已經係第3日!!<br />\n今時今日既你 望著呢班學生<br />\n為左成個香港既去打呢場戰爭<br />\n你 仲可以唔罷工咩?<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG 原POST :<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1711180/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1711180/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1711315/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1711315/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1709831/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1709831/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1709918/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1709918/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1711267/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1711267/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1710239/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1710239/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1710026/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1710026/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"49e359c05e013ce084c1974114df0ff46ffbeb2b","tid":1712683,"uid":125760,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VTiG